{"tid":160336,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]拿磚狂砸母親頭致死　子：不想再養她了","createTime":"2017-03-17T15:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T17:48:06.000Z","uid":32407,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e9d0d9b65aaa1499213796fdc47fbb66860d0d9","tid":160336,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:37:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://tw.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170317/bkncn-20170317172301817-0317_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170317%2Fbkncn-20170317172301817-0317_05011_001.html&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=8d52deb0\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170317/bkncn-20170317172301817-0317_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n安徽阜陽72歲王鳳仙本月7日凌晨慘遭喝醉的兒子用磚狂砸頭部，最終因顱骨粉碎性骨折，當場死亡。事後，其兒子康豐竟供稱自己殺害母親，是因為「不想再養她了」。目前，康豐已被依法刑事拘留，案件正進一步辦理之中。<br />\n<br />\n本月7日凌晨3時許，康豐喝醉後和母親發生爭執，在爭執過程中，他隨手拿起屋內的磚頭，多次撃打母親頭部，最終令母親顱骨粉碎性骨折，顱腦損傷，慘死兒子手下。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，王鳳仙育有兩名兒子，此前因贍養母親的問題，兩名兒子訴諸法院，法院判定王鳳仙由46歲的兒子康豐贍養。康豐的妻子及小孩都在外地打工，只有他獨自在家照顧母親。可是，康豐長期酗酒，加上因家中土地分配及贍養母親的事，經常與母親爭執，曾多次毆打她。<br />\n<br />\n康豐落網後供稱，自己之所以殺害母親，是因為「不想再養她了」。他又認為不用在家照顧母親，自己就可以外出打工掙錢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c753707f333d9709da7fcb21fc69e87f20fb404c","tid":160336,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfec9c9bbe55b9ba87de7a795e3466d7913ce340","tid":160336,"uid":86378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:39:34.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 